data.description: ''Elegant Mediterranean Brick Home in Prime LocationNestled in one of Albuquerque's most sought-after neighborhoods, this exquisite Mediterranean brick home combines timeless style with modern luxury. Situated on a spacious 1/3-acre corner lot, the property boasts mature landscaping and a secluded backyard oasis, creating a private haven in the heart of the city.The home's classic brick exterior, accented by large windows, floods the space with natural light and lends a sense of grandeur. Stepping inside, the spacious and elegantly appointed interior features gleaming hardwood floors, detailed ceiling crown molding, and a striking fireplace that serves as the centerpiece of the main living area. A formal sitting area offers serene views of the lush backyard.
